data.description: Lovely, updated home in the Sierra neighborhood just off of West Beach. Spacious open concept main living area with vaulted ceiling & luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. Kitchen boasts quartz countertops, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances plus seating at the peninsula. Dining area enjoys a built-in buffet. Newer vanities with vessel sink in both bathrooms. Sierra Country Club amenities include a pool, clubhouse, activities and events. You will love the beach access and Olympic Mountain views. Fort Ebey state park is just around the corner with picnic areas & miles of hiking and biking trails. Great location between the quaint town of Coupeville and Oak Harbor with easy access to Hwy 20 and NAS Whidbey.
